Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:24.61,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}仅仅为了寻求奇迹的降临
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:29.66,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}彷徨于无尽的黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:33.53,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}身陷于此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:40.51,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}将再也见不到未来光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:43.17,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今宵明月邀我为伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.81,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}即便仍道不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:49.97,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}心中早已呐喊无数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:55.97,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}埋藏心底的感情发出悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:03:00.90,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}牢握这份坚定的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:06.54,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}多么希望变强哪怕一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:13.36,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}天空 振翅飞跃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:21.36,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}未来 触手可及
