Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:19.73,SAOED2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}高高伸展双臂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:26.96,SAOED2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}展翅飞向那片柔光
